title.narrative: Strengthened production of gender statistics to enable the monitoring of national policies and reporting commitments under the SDGs

description.narrative: This outcome aims to increase the production of quality, and comparable gender statistics to address gender data gaps and meet policy and reporting commitments under the SDGs, the Convention on the Elimination of All Forms of Discrimination against Women (CEDAW) and the Beijing Platform for Action.
